      "text": "describe(\"drag-drop @file: paste\", () =\u003e {\n  it(\"wraps an existing file path dropped into the input buffer\", async () =\u003e {\n    await withDriver",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/chat/commands/file-paste.test.ts\n\ndescribe(\"drag-drop @file: paste\", () =\u003e {\n  it(\"wraps an existing file path dropped into the input buffer\", async () =\u003e {\n    await withDriver",
